        <h2>How to Check Your 2024 Scores on the Univindia Portal: Step-by-Step</h2>
        <p>Checking your result on the official portal is designed to be a straightforward process. However, during the declaration of major 2024 results (like BA Final or B.Sc Final), the site can experience unprecedented traffic. Follow these steps for the best experience:</p>
